<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF">}</span></span></code></pre>
<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p><strong>第四步: 在项目根目录中,创建一个如下的脚本文件<code v-pre>deploy.sh</code></strong></p>
<div class="language-sh line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="shiki" data-ext="sh" data-title="sh" style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#abb2bf;--shiki-light-bg:#FAFAFA;--shiki-dark-bg:#282c34"><pre v-pre class="shiki shiki-themes one-light one-dark-pro vp-code"><code><span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#A0A1A7;--shiki-light-font-style:italic;--shiki-dark:#7F848E;--shiki-dark-font-style:italic">#!/usr/bin/env sh</span></span>
